%H A230640 Max A. Alekseyev and N. J. A. Sloane, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2112.14365">On Kaprekar's Junction Numbers</a>, arXiv:2112.14365, 2021; Journal of Combinatorics and Number Theory 12:3 (2022), 115-155.
